davy-lamp (former known as monitor) is a ruby-on-rails based HTTP web server monitoring web app


to make use of it replace all "example.com" in the sourcecode with the domain where the app will be running.

to make use of the reverse monitoring feature make sure to setup the heartbeat subdomain and the each minute runnung cron-job targeting run_cron.sh





